#1. Program greeting.

print("\nWelcome to Band Name Generator!!! \nThis program will help you name your new band?\n")

#2. Ask the user for the city that they grew up in.

city = input("In what city did you grow up?\n")

#3. Ask the user for the name of a pet.

pet = input("What is a name of one of your pets?\n")

#4. Combine the name of their city and pet and show them their band name.

print("\nYour band's name is " + city + pet+"\n Have fun Jammin'!!!")
#5. make sure the input cursor shows on a new line.



